，又因為你從未得到過滿足，實在是一個死症循環。<br />\n又不能幫你一把，又不能推你一把，更不能把心一橫置之不理，從見到有人自殺起，我嘅心已經不舒服了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28790b64a7228409fa6556d5f5e45a8670cba35","tid":746920,"uid":36607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2ae6213f2dea63e09ad2f246a5d6baf8d0fe49f","tid":746920,"uid":191450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f01261048af6658410bb05a5f8b371336cd8ffa","tid":746920,"uid":162270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0280b165495e726a80abd42ccd135d200d599fa","tid":746920,"uid":191450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"但係缺氧都係死腦胞"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"但係你個腦唔知所以你都唔會有咩感覺<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T07:19:37.000Z","msg":"正確 但講緊未遂嘅情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"咁應該算係最舒服？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}